COLLECTION_DESCRIPTION: This command will display your entire collection, which can then be sorted and filtered in various ways. Using this command with additional prompts will open the embed with the specific filter already applied to it. Use the prompt "t:ut" in addition to this command to highlight all cards in your collection that currently don't have a tag. Use {{prefix}}help filter command to see all available filters

SLASH_DESC2: Enter the filters you want to apply to the collection
